description: Bringing your sweet tooth some good emotions, it must be Sweet Commotion!This mobile bakery specializes in Lefse, a traditional Norwegian flatbread that's perfectly designed to be flavored in a number of delicious ways. When you put that together with all of their other baked delicacies, you can see why this food truck is fast becoming the talk of the town.Treat yourself to something terrific today, with the help of the fine folks at Sweet Commotion.
name: Sweet Commotion
